# Pull Request

## Title
Implement Goal Icon Picker

## Summary
This pull request adds support for goal icons in the CommBank Goal Tracker application.

### Changes made
- Added support for storing an icon in the Goal model.
- Implemented the PUT request to update goals through the API.
- Completed the emoji selection handler (`pickEmojiOnClick`) so selected emojis are saved.
- Updated the Goal Manager to allow selecting and updating goal icons.
- Updated Goal Cards to display the selected icon.
- Verified that icon changes persist after refreshing the application.
- Created a feature branch (`feature/goal-icons`) for development.
